<dl id="n12115m"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12115m">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12115m"> 115(m)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Peace! <font face="wake">D</font> <small>Green</small></blockquote> <dd class="well"> <ul class="list-inline" id="n12115m"> <li>FW unlocated</li> </ul> <blockquote class="sources">Sa premi&egrave;re parole est une parole de paix: &ldquo;La paix soit avec vous!&rdquo; n&apos;est-ce pas le souhait que le Sauveur ressuscit&eacute; adressait &agrave; ses disciples? mais cette paix, pour le vaillant athl&egrave;te, n&apos;est point le nonchaloir qui s&apos;endort dans une fallacieuse s&eacute;curit&eacute; &hellip; <br><font color="green">[His first word is a word of peace: &ldquo;May peace be with you!&rdquo; isn&apos;t that what the resurrected Saviour told his disciples? but this peace, for the brave athlete, is hardly the indolent who falls asleep as a result of a false feeling of security &hellip;]</font> <small> <a name="STCM" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#STCM"><cite title="source">Saint Colomban</cite></a> (1905) 121</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Note: See also: <a name="n12024e" href="n12all.htm#n12024e">N12 (VI.B.14):024(e)</a> for 424.26</mm> </dd></dl>
